{"tid":478596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊攻入港鐵 料最快下月可用微信支付買車票","createTime":"2017-11-24T08:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T10:26:22.000Z","uid":284,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4db88bb49a3ecd52e7ae075954d7063540ef615c","tid":478596,"uid":284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"騰訊（00700）擴大本地移動支付應用範圍，公布與港鐵（00066）達成合作協議，用戶以後可透過微信支付搭地鐵。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊指，正式與港鐵簽署合作協議，雙方就微信支付及WeChat Pay HK（微信香港錢包），在港鐵的移動支付業務合作。換言之，無論內地遊客或本地人，均可以微信支付購買車票。<br />\n<br />\n惟公告無進一步披露合作形式、用法和時間，港鐵回應查詢時表示，12月中會推行試驗計劃，先在1至2個車站的售票機新增更多電子支付功能。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，合作初期乘客仍未能用微信支付直接「拍手機」入閘。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，廣州地鐵亦由上周起與微信支付合作。用戶只需透過微信小程序中的「廣州地鐵乘車碼」，將QR Code拍向閘機，即可入閘乘坐地鐵。<br />\n<br />\n其他國家亦有類似用法，以英國為例，現時倫敦地鐵亦接受乘客以Apple Pay、Android Pay等手機方式付款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://invest.hket.com/article/1954284/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1954284%2F&d=mFMdzWpOsUGUWZ56RlTWqgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=a312b2e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://invest.hket.com/article/1954284/</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c3bf61df45197f84b17d9855aad2e5e09f2393","tid":478596,"uid":86756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"In 700 we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升爆佢老母個臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814292188cbad